# thelakesvegas.com (project rules)

- **Stack:** Next.js 15 App Router, React 19, TypeScript, Tailwind. Import alias `@/*` → `src/*`.
- **Before finishing a change:** run `npm run lint`, `npm run type-check`, and `npm run build` when you touch app code (same as CI).
- **Secrets:** Never commit `.env` / `.env.local`. Document new env vars in `.env.example` only (placeholders).
- **IDX:** Do not edit `src/components/idx/*` without explicit MLS/IDX approval.
- **RealScout:** Script once in root layout; CSP must include `em.realscout.com` and `www.realscout.com` in `script-src` and `connect-src` if adjusting headers.
- **SEO/NAP:** Keep visible business name, address, phone, hours, and JSON-LD aligned with GBP when changing `site-config` or location copy.
- **Style:** Smallest change that works; mirror existing components and file layout in `src/app/` and `src/components/`.
- **Context:** See repo root `AGENTS.md` for paths and commands.
